  "text": "Taken together, our results confirm previous studies in the literature of young people at risk for schizophrenia, (McIntosh et al, 2011,; Bhojraj et al, 2011a Bhojraj et al, , 2011b [CITATION_1] ) and also take them further to show that these findings are specifically present in people who satisfy a more narrow definition for being at genetic high risk, i.e. having likely inheritance of the disorder.",
